'''2013年博拉茲詹地震'''是一起發生於當地時間2013年11月28日17時21分（[[UTC+3:30|UTC+3:30]]）的地震。根據[[美國地質調查局|美國地質調查局]]，[[震央|震央]]位在[[伊朗|伊朗]][[博拉茲詹|博拉茲詹]]東北方14公里處，而規模達到5.6，震源深度則約16.4公里（10.2英里）<ref>{{cite web | url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/usb000l7nt#summary | title=M5.6 - 14km NE of Borazjan, Iran | publisher=[[美國地質調查局|美國地質調查局]] | date=2013-11-28 | accessdate=2013-11-28 | archive-date=2013-11-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131130034840/http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/usb000l7nt#summary | dead-url=no }}</ref>。此次地震所引發的災害造成7人死亡，45人受傷<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://rt.com/news/iran-bushehr-region-earthquake-450/ |title=7 dead, 45 injured as 5.6 earthquake hits 60km from Iran’s Bushehr nuclear plant |date=2013-11-28 |accessdate=2013-11-28 |archive-date=2018-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180413124705/https://www.rt.com/news/iran-bushehr-region-earthquake-450/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2013/11/28/337168/quake-kills-7-injures-30-in-south-iran/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-10-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151003151656/http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2013/11/28/337168/quake-kills-7-injures-30-in-south-iran/ |archivedate=2015-10-03 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2013/11/deadly-quake-hits-near-iran-nuclear-plant-20131128182030129826.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-11-28 |archive-date=2020-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919200000/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2013/11/deadly-quake-hits-near-iran-nuclear-plant-20131128182030129826.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://voiceofrussia.com/news/2013_11_28/Quake-near-Irans-Bushehr-kills-7-injures-30-emergency-chief-9443/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-11-28 |archive-date=2014-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140727102045/http://voiceofrussia.com/news/2013_11_28/Quake-near-Irans-Bushehr-kills-7-injures-30-emergency-chief-9443/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-iran-quake/seven-killed-in-iran-quake-no-damage-to-nuclear-station-reported-idUSBRE9AR0O120131128 |title=Seven killed in Iran quake, no damage to nuclear station reported |publisher=Reuters |date=2013-11-28 |accessdate=2018-01-19 |archive-date=2019-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190909064802/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-iran-quake/seven-killed-in-iran-quake-no-damage-to-nuclear-station-reported-idUSBRE9AR0O120131128 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

